thread.title: Deborah Anderson

author: Deborah Anderson
title: Deborah Anderson
text:
Shane contacted me the same day to go over the process of OpenAgent. I must say he had a great vision of clear direction and explained every detail off what to expect. He recommeded 3 Top Agents and sent my information out to them and within 2 hours I heard Back from Ashley from RayWhite who I must say done a amazing job going through all the process from appraisal of my home to the cost of buying and selling.
Unfortunately the other 2 Agents do not bother to contact me which was disappointing.
